<strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ellie3-gimmick-free">原作者的更多作品！</a></strong></p>
<p>這是我的<strong>第一篇 GOI 格式！</strong></p>
<h5 id="toc0"><span>Yay!</span></h5>
<p>圖片來源：<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Hausziege_02.jpg">Here!</a><br />
攝影師：Armin Kübelbeck, CC-BY-SA 3.0</p>
<p>譯者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4357011); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4357011&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601644373" alt="feitag" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4357011)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4357011); return false;">feitag</a></span></p>
</div>
